{"tid":1790960,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"賀一誠：未有足夠人才和法例建立金融中心","createTime":"2019-12-20T11:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T15:58:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":143,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"eb27a74125fb679bdbdf33dd71b1f77c277af795","tid":1790960,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"剛上任的澳門行政長官賀一誠，回應在今次澳門回歸20周年慶典前，有多名香港記者被拒入境的事件，他說警方有自己的指引，尊重警方的決定。<br />\n<br />\n至於國家主席習近平在就職禮講話中，提到不容許任何外部勢力干擾澳門內部事務，澳門會否加強入境措施，賀一誠說不會，但會堅決執行不讓外部勢力干擾澳門內部事務。<br />\n<br />\n賀一誠回答記者問題時又說，無聽過中央有大禮送給澳門，澳門暫時未有足夠人才和法例，建立外界所指的金融中心。<br />\n<br />\n他強調會和新一屆政府認真落實指示要求，推進澳門特色一國兩制成功實踐，行穩致遠。"},{"pid":"d32cca4092c748aa9b7344e3e2b2e688eb4dcd28","tid":1790960,"uid":1891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3113939113fc2590b2999d64bfab78da0fb7508b","tid":1790960,"uid":173207,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"咁誠實！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8325340bf81b416538bc324dd958196d941768da","tid":1790960,"uid":189046,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"賀你一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c79759f356e0566c1df9fa2c9511528ae76419","tid":1790960,"uid":47112,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:34:30.000Z","